    <p>
        <m>{\color{blue} \textbf{The key importance of studying Scale drawing}}</m>.
    </p>
    <p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <p>
                   Scale drawings help represent objects proportionally. 
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Understanding scales allows us to determine actual measurements accurately.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Scale drawings are essential in many fields, such as architecture, design, and geography.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
